name: Undercover (V)
Lore: 'The Empire maintains a network of spies attempting to infiltrate the Rebel Alliance or misinform their operatives.',
Text: 'Deploy on your spy at a site. Spy is now Undercover. During your control phase, may take one Informant into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. At same and related sites, opponent''s [Permanent Weapon] weapon destiny draws are -1 (-2 if targeting this character). (Immune to Alter.)',
